### ============================================
### 1. CREAR ÓRDENES (POST)
### ============================================

### 1.1 Crear orden con 1 detalle (Libro 1: Clean Code x 2)
POST http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "ref": "ORD001",
  "idClient": 1001,
  "startDate": "2026-04-16 18:30:00",
  "description": "Primer pedido - Libros de programación",
  "address": "Calle Mayor 10",
  "name": "Juan Perez",
  "phone": "600112233",
  "shopcartDetails": [
    {
      "bookId": 1,
      "amount": 2,
      "price": 39.99,
      "discount": 0.10
    }
  ]
}

### 1.2 Crear orden con múltiples detalles (Libro 1 + Libro 2)
POST http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "ref": "ORD002",
  "idClient": 1001,
  "startDate": "2026-04-17 10:00:00",
  "description": "Segundo pedido - Compra variada",
  "address": "Calle Mayor 10",
  "name": "Juan Perez",
  "phone": "600112233",
  "shopcartDetails": [
    {
      "bookId": 1,
      "amount": 1,
      "price": 39.99,
      "discount": 0.05
    },
    {
      "bookId": 2,
      "amount": 3,
      "price": 24.99,
      "discount": 0.15
    }
  ]
}

### 1.3 Crear orden con XML
POST http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders
Content-Type: application/xml
Accept: application/xml

<order>
    <ref>ORD003</ref>
    <idClient>1001</idClient>
    <startDate>2026-04-18T09:15:00</startDate>
    <description>Tercer pedido - Formato XML</description>
    <address>Calle Mayor 10</address>
    <name>Juan Perez</name>
    <phone>600112233</phone>
    <shopcartDetails>
        <orderDetail>
            <bookId>2</bookId>
            <amount>2</amount>
            <price>24.99</price>
            <discount>0.20</discount>
        </orderDetail>
    </shopcartDetails>
</order>

### ============================================
### 2. OBTENER ÓRDENES (GET)
### ============================================

### 2.1 Obtener orden ORD001 (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders/ORD001
Accept: application/json

### 2.2 Obtener orden ORD001 (XML)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders/ORD001
Accept: application/xml

### 2.3 Obtener orden ORD002 (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders/ORD002
Accept: application/json

### 2.4 Obtener orden ORD002 (XML)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders/ORD002
Accept: application/xml

### 2.5 Obtener orden ORD003 (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders/ORD003
Accept: application/json

### 2.6 Obtener orden ORD003 (XML)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders/ORD003
Accept: application/xml

### ============================================
### 3. ACTUALIZAR ÓRDENES (PUT)
### ============================================

### 3.1 Actualizar ORD001: Cambiar detalles (JSON)
PUT http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders/ORD001
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "ref": "ORD001",
  "idClient": 1001,
  "startDate": "2026-04-16 18:30:00",
  "description": "Pedido actualizado - Nueva cantidad",
  "address": "Calle Mayor 10",
  "name": "Juan Perez",
  "phone": "600112233",
  "shopcartDetails": [
    {
      "bookId": 1,
      "amount": 3,
      "price": 39.99,
      "discount": 0.15
    }
  ]
}

### 3.2 Actualizar ORD002: Agregar otro libro (JSON)
PUT http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders/ORD002
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "ref": "ORD002",
  "idClient": 1001,
  "startDate": "2026-04-17 10:00:00",
  "description": "Pedido actualizado - Agregar detalle",
  "address": "Calle Mayor 10",
  "name": "Juan Perez",
  "phone": "600112233",
  "shopcartDetails": [
    {
      "bookId": 1,
      "amount": 2,
      "price": 39.99,
      "discount": 0.05
    },
    {
      "bookId": 2,
      "amount": 4,
      "price": 24.99,
      "discount": 0.15
    }
  ]
}

### 3.3 Actualizar ORD003: Cambiar con XML
PUT http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders/ORD003
Content-Type: application/xml
Accept: application/xml

<order>
    <ref>ORD003</ref>
    <idClient>1001</idClient>
    <startDate>2026-04-18T09:15:00</startDate>
    <description>Pedido actualizado - XML</description>
    <address>Calle Mayor 10</address>
    <name>Juan Perez</name>
    <phone>600112233</phone>
    <shopcartDetails>
        <orderDetail>
            <bookId>1</bookId>
            <amount>5</amount>
            <price>39.99</price>
            <discount>0.25</discount>
        </orderDetail>
        <orderDetail>
            <bookId>2</bookId>
            <amount>2</amount>
            <price>24.99</price>
            <discount>0.10</discount>
        </orderDetail>
    </shopcartDetails>
</order>

### 3.4 Verificar actualización de ORD001
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders/ORD001
Accept: application/json

